      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="ic">🌍</div>
          <h3>Linguistic Equity</h3>
          <p>Every indigenous language deserves a complete, computable numeric index &mdash; standardized, cite-able, and freely usable by its own speakers and the world.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="ic">🔓</div>
          <h3>Open Scholarly Infrastructure</h3>
          <p>All entries are published under open licence: crawlable, machine-readable, and structured as scholarly datasets with JSON-LD Dataset schema.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="ic">🧠</div>
          <h3>AI &amp; NLP Ready</h3>
          <p>Training-grade corpora for the next generation of multilingual language models, translation systems, and culturally grounded educational AI.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

